1077
00:44:16,790 --> 00:44:17,990
Saya akan menerimanya untuk Huan'er.

1078
00:44:18,100 --> 00:44:18,910
Terima kasih, Tian Chi.

1079
00:44:23,790 --> 00:44:24,470
Adakah

1080
00:44:24,700 --> 00:44:25,620
apa-apa lagi yang anda perlukan?

1081
00:44:27,120 --> 00:44:28,370
Anda belum makan lagi, kan?

1082
00:44:28,430 --> 00:44:29,100
